'''Nurse attorneys''' are individuals who are licensed as both [[lawyer]]s and [[nurse]]s. Nurse attorneys are found in a number of practice areas including academia, [[administrative law]], litigation, risk management & [[patient safety]], and regulatory compliance.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://taana.org/Career-Paths|title=TAANA Executive Office - Career Paths|publisher=}}</ref>

